Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.71,Default,AYUMI,0,0,0,,.يُوجد شخصٌ مثلك
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.44,Default,CONAN,0,0,0,,هاه؟
